# dfa-game
## Controls
- left click - create state or drag state to new position
- right click - create edge by clicking on start state and clicking on end state
- middle click - delete state
- 0 - switch transition character to 0
- 1 - switch transition character to 1
- e - toggle accept state for state mouse is over
- s - set start state for state mouse is over

## Test Input
1. hover mouse over input box at top
2. type 0's or 1's and backspace to delete
3. press enter to print result of running input on DFA to terminal